name: Welcome to wiremoons.com
body:
## Welcome to wiremoons.com

### About

This site is a jump point for wiremoons.com, and is hosted on GitHub as a redirect to [wiremoons.github.io](https://wiremoons.github.io/). Please see the links in the section below for other sites I post content too as well.

'wiremoons' is an anagram for Simon Rowe - which is my name.

### My Other Internet Sites

- [Flickr - main site for photographs](https://www.flickr.com/photos/wiremoons/)
- [Tumblr - mlog and more casual photos](http://wiremoons.tumblr.com/)
- [GitHub - my development projects and code](https://github.com/wiremoons)
- [Twitter - news and social media](https://twitter.com/wiremoons)
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
